{"title":"积肥施肥农谚","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":11,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥施肥农谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流不尽的水，积不完的肥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊扫帚响，粪堆长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊猪粪、红花草，农家两个宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊种田不养猪，一定有一输。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊家里土，地里虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊人靠饭饱，田靠肥料。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊肥料足，多收谷，一熟顶二熟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊人哄地皮，地哄肚皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊勤起勤垫，十天一圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊秀才要读书，种田要养猪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊庄稼一枝花，全靠粪当家。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}